---
import Starburst from "../components/icons/Starburst.astro";
import AE from "../components/icons/AE.astro";
import YouTube from "../components/YouTube.astro";
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>Astro</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<main>
			<section>
				<div class="section-heading">
					<Starburst />
					<h2>Section One</h2>
				</div>
				<p>
					This section was written by a man who knows what he's doing
					and has definitely never been bitten by a moose. Special
					thanks to the assistant night-watchman of the Bolivian
					Ministry of Silly Walks, who provided neither assistance nor
					walks but did supply the biscuits. All rights reserved,
					except the ones that weren't, which is most of them.
				</p>
				<p>
					The producers would like to apologize for the previous
					paragraph. It was written during a period of high humidity
					and low biscuit availability, and does not reflect the views
					of the management, the under-management, or the surprisingly
					opinionated tea trolley on the third floor.
				</p>
			</section>
			<section>
				<div class="section-heading">
					<AE />
					<h2>Section Two</h2>
				</div>
				<p>
					No llamas were consulted in the making of this section,
					though three did submit written comments, all of which said
					"splendid." The font was chosen after a rigorous process
					involving a blindfold, a dartboard, and a strongly worded
					letter from the typographer's second cousin, who remains at
					large.
				</p>
				<p>
					This section is dedicated to everyone who has ever filled
					out a form in triplicate only to be told the correct form is
					a completely different form, also in triplicate, available
					from a window that is only open on alternate Tuesdays during
					a leap year. You are not alone. You are, however, in the
					wrong queue.
				</p>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2>Section Three</h2>
				<YouTube id="8v-O9B-UYUc" title="Section Three Video" />
				<p>
					The knights who say "Ni" have reviewed this section and
					found it satisfactory, pending the addition of one
					shrubbery. The shrubbery has been ordered but is currently
					delayed due to unforeseen circumstances involving a very
					small cart, an overly ambitious hedgehog, and the ongoing
					reorganization of the entire shrubbery logistics department.
				</p>
				<p>
					In conclusion, nobody expected this section to exist, least
					of all the Spanish Inquisition, whose chief weapons are
					surprise, fear, ruthless efficiency, and an almost fanatical
					devotion to accurate page margins. All measurements are
					approximate. The page is not responsible for any
					disappointment experienced while reading to this point.
				</p>
			</section>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	html,
	body {
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
		min-height: 100vh;
	}

	body {
		background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #0a0a0a 0%, #2e2e2e 100%);
		color: #e8e8e8;
		font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
	}

	main {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 2rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	section {
		border: 1px solid #aaaaaa;
		border-radius: 12px;
		padding: 2rem;
	}

	.section-heading {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.section-heading h2 {
		margin: 0;
	}
</style>
